  <description>
    <p>
      NOTE: 15 seconds after launch the default browser will open with bliss.
    </p>
    <p>
      What if your music collection looked as good as it sounds?
      bliss makes your music library more browsable, searchable, playable and beautiful,
      whichever music players you use.
    </p>
    <p>
      bliss performs all the hard work in organizing your music collection; making it consistent,
      correct and complete with little effort.
    </p>
    <p>
      Imagine defining simple rules by which your music library is managed, and then having
      a sidekick use those rules to resolve inconsistencies, fill missing information and artwork,
      and correct wrong data.
    </p>
    <p>
       bliss applies these rules forever, aligning new music with your library,
       or implementing new rules across your collection as your music players change. 
    </p>
  </description>

